    "title": "Urban LST Downscaling over Kinshasa",
    "description": "A proof-of-concept workflow for downscaling ESA CCI Land Surface Temperature from 1 km to 10 m resolution using XGBoost, trained on Sentinel-2 spectral indices, WSF3D building morphology, and terrain derivatives across 15 African cities. Applied to Kinshasa for 2016 and 2023 to assess urban-driven LST change.",
